	(297,6,'2017-03-14 10:55:51','2017-03-14 10:55:51','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With more than 21 years of experience at the helm of multi award-winning </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dentistry</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> magazine and numerous other dental journals. As editorial director of FMC, Julian is a well-known face in dental publishing. He is also a member of the editorial committee of the British Dental Industry Association (BDIA).</span>','Julian English: Introduction to digital dentistry','','draft','closed','closed','','julian-english-introduction-to-digital-dentistry','','','2017-08-15 14:27:11','2017-08-15 13:27:11','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=speakers&#038;p=297',0,'speakers','',0),
