	(1244,6,'2018-01-25 15:56:10','2018-01-25 15:56:10','Dealing with accuracy, reliability and productivity is a challenge for all teams. Marco Heidel, MDT. (Zirkonzahn), will explain the modern concept of Computer Dental Diagnostic. By demonstrating patient cases, he will perform an in-depth analysis of the latest state-of-the-art devices for a smooth, individual workflow, from digital patient analysis to the final restoration. Marco will show a revolutionary approach to capture the patient’s reference planes and to reproduce 1:1 analogue data into the software through a photo-realistic 3D digitisation of the patient’s face, resulting in a 100% individual and reproducible restoration. This method permits to work on the always-accessible virtual patient reducing the error rate and the number of meetings at the practice. A new computer-based guided implant planning solution allowing for backward planning and the following immediate loading of implants will also be outlined.\r\n\r\n<strong>Since August 2016</strong>\r\nSteger dental laboratory (Zirkonzahn), Brunico, Italy.\r\nCourse instructor in practical and digital dental technology in South Tyrol and worldwide.\r\nResearch and development collaborator.\r\n\r\n<strong>2014 – 2015</strong><strong>\r\n</strong>Master school of dental technology, Erfurt, Germany\r\nTraining as master dental technician, technical commercial-craft and trainer\r\n\r\n<strong>2010 – 2014</strong>\r\n“Pötzsch” dental laboratory, Dresden, Germany\r\nDental technician in all dental technical fields, CAD/CAM, organisation-planning-consultation\r\n\r\n<strong>2008 – 2009</strong>\r\nLuciano Gaddi dental laboratory, Reggio Emilia, Italy\r\nCAD/CAM, aesthetic and functional all-ceramic restorations and implant restorations\r\n\r\n<strong>2008</strong>\r\nMy Dental laboratory, Altenberg, Germany\r\nDental technician in all technical fields and CAD/CAM','Marco Heidel: Computer Dental Diagnostic - 11:00-11:30','','publish','closed','closed','','marco-heidel-computer-dental-diagnostic','','','2018-09-12 11:05:27','2018-09-12 10:05:27','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=speakers&#038;p=1244',0,'speakers','',0),
